								<li><strong>Q: How scary are the attractions?</strong></li>
								<li>A: The Hayride can be enjoyed by the whole family. It is a low-medium intensity haunt but still has it's fair share of scares and surprises. The Forgotten Forest and Psychosis are high intensity haunts with many scares. Zombie Assault is a simulator and features many virtual scares and action sequences.</li>
